
== Building the YANG Tools ==


1. Checkout the latest version from yangtools.git - [[OpenDaylight_Controller:Pulling,_Hacking,_and_Pushing_the_Code_from_the_CLI]]

2. Build all packages

    mvn clean install

== Running Demo ==

1. Go into the folder for builded API code generator

    cd code-generator\samples\modeling-sample

2. Folder contains preconfigured sample (see pom.xml) for toaster.yang model
** pom.xml contains configuration for project and code generation plugin
** src/main/yang/toaster.yang contains YANG model of toaster

3. Run to build project 
    mvn clean install

4. Generated sources of Java interfaces describing DTOs are in target/generated-sources/sal folder.

